# Tutti dev reload after agent-chat changes

When you finish modifying code in this `agent-chat` repository (unless the user explicitly says not to), run:

```bash
pnpm dev:tutti:reload
```

This rebuilds the web/server bundle, updates the dev catalog artifact, and makes the new version available in Tutti App Center.

After reload, tell the user the new dev version (from script output, e.g. `0.1.17-dev.45`) and remind them to refresh App Center / reinstall Group Chat if Tutti does not auto-update.

Do not skip this step when delivering implementation work that touches runtime UI or server behavior.
